WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.733 --> 00:00:01.533
Mom

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.033
To risk my mother's life as evil

3
00:00:04.366 --> 00:00:06.233
As expected of you, you are the king

4
00:00:06.366 --> 00:00:08.266
To a rebel like you

5
00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:09.666
No need to consider other

6
00:00:09.666 --> 00:00:12.866
Today can bring your mother and son together for a long life

7
00:00:12.866 --> 00:00:14.200
Have mercy

8
00:00:14.666 --> 00:00:17.933
But for the sake of your mother-son love

9
00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:20.266
I can give you a chance

10
00:00:20.266 --> 00:00:21.266
His Royal Highness

11
00:00:21.266 --> 00:00:22.600
Don't talk to them

12
00:00:22.766 --> 00:00:24.633
Quickly execute them all

13
00:00:24.766 --> 00:00:26.166
These traitors

14
00:00:26.333 --> 00:00:28.666
It's not worth talking to you at all

15
00:00:28.866 --> 00:00:29.666
Haoran

16
00:00:30.266 --> 00:00:32.500
Leave me alone

17
00:00:33.266 --> 00:00:34.100
Don't believe it.

18
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:36.000
Opportunity for what?

19
00:00:36.533 --> 00:00:37.766
Come here.

20
00:00:40.533 --> 00:00:42.966
I didn't tell you to come over.

21
00:00:43.366 --> 00:00:44.300
kneel

22
00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:46.366
Kneel down Haoran

23
00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:47.666
Don't kneel

24
00:00:48.300 --> 00:00:49.100
Do not kneel

25
00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:50.666
Good idea.

26
00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:55.433
Kneel down and confess your crimes

27
00:00:55.466 --> 00:00:57.966
For the sake of my father's benevolent governance

28
00:00:58.666 --> 00:01:01.066
I could consider letting you go

29
00:01:04.566 --> 00:01:06.633
Haoran is not allowed to return

30
00:01:07.400 --> 00:01:08.800
My Lin family

31
00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:11.000
Men stand tall

32
00:01:11.066 --> 00:01:13.500
I was like this little head down.

33
00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.466
Haoran, listen to me

34
00:01:17.266 --> 00:01:18.266
People are a family

35
00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:20.300
I would rather die standing

36
00:01:20.333 --> 00:01:22.033
Don't live on your knees

